Here are few tips for getting an accurate face scan measurements :
1) Find a well-lit area and stand or sit still during the assessment.
2) Make sure your face is fully visible and not covered by anything like a mask or hat.
3) Try to stay calm and focused during the assessment.
4) Don\'t let direct sunlight shine on the camera or area in the frame.
5) Place your phone on stable surface or use a stand to get a reliable reading.
6) It would take 2–3 minutes to complete the assessment.
